Package: nuclei
Version: 3.11.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, golang
Section: web
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://nuclei.projectdiscovery.io/
Description: Fast and customizable vulnerability scanner
 nuclei is used to send requests across targets based on a template
 leading to zero false positives and providing fast scanning
 for known paths. It is built with simplicity in mind.
